OL,3,CJury fail to reach verdict in trial of
OL,4,Cbrothers accused of assaulting officer
OL,6,FA jury has been unable to reach a
OL,7,Fverdict in the retrial of two brothers
OL,8,Faccused of assaulting a police officer
OL,9,Fat a busy airport.
OL,11,FMohammed Fahir Amaaz, 21, and Muhammad
OL,12,FAmaad, 26, have both been on trial at
OL,13,FLiverpool Crown Court over allegations
OL,14,Fthey inflicted a "high level of
OL,15,Fviolence" when they assaulted PC
OL,16,FZachary Marsden causing actual bodily
OL,17,Fharm at Manchester Airport on 23 July
OL,18,F2024.
OL,26,@vD@ROUwD@IO]
