OL,3,CJury fail to reach verdict in trial of
OL,4,Cbrothers accused of assaulting officer
OL,6,FAt a previous trial, Amaaz was found
OL,7,Fguilty of assaulting a member of the
OL,8,Fpublic and two female police officers
OL,9,Fduring an incident which later went
OL,10,Fviral on social media.
OL,12,FBut the jury at Liverpool Crown Court,
OL,13,Fwho spent 10 hours deliberating in
OL,14,FJuly 2025, could not reach a verdict
OL,15,Fon the allegations the brothers
OL,16,Fassaulted PC Zachary Marsden.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
