PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779304272
OL,3,CJury fail to reach verdict in trial of
OL,4,Cbrothers accused of assaulting officer
OL,6,FFollowing a retrial, on Wednesday 20
OL,7,FMay, jurors said they also could not
OL,8,Fagree on any verdicts in respect of
OL,9,Feither of the defendants after
OL,10,Fdeliberating for almost 20 hours.
OL,12,FDismissing the 12, the judge thanked
OL,13,Fthe eight women and four men for their
OL,14,F"hard work" over five weeks.
OL,16,FProsecutors asked the judge for time
OL,17,Fto consider their position and to
OL,18,Fdecide whether they will seek another
OL,19,Fre-trial. A further hearing has been
OL,20,Fscheduled for 29 May.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@KO]
